# BODYBVILDER 💪

**AI-Powered Bodybuilding Form Coach**

Real-time pose estimation & rep counting for 31 exercises — right from your browser.

🌐 **Live App:** [bodybvilder.vercel.app](https://bodybvilder.vercel.app)

---

## Features

- 🤖 **AI Form Analysis** — MediaPipe pose detection scores your form in real-time
- 📊 **Rep Counter** — Automatic rep counting for every exercise
- 🔥 **Streak Tracking** — Daily workout streaks to keep you consistent
- 📈 **Stats Dashboard** — Weekly chart, total reps, workout history
- 🎨 **4 Themes** — Dark, Light, Cyber, Sunset
- 📱 **PWA** — Install on phone like a native app
- 🏋️ **31 Exercises** — Chest, Back, Shoulders, Triceps, Biceps, Legs, Core

---

## Tech Stack

- **React 18** with React Router v6
- **MediaPipe Pose** — real-time body landmark detection
- **CSS Variables** — multi-theme system
- **LocalStorage** — no backend needed, fully offline
- **Vercel** — deployment

---

## Getting Started

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start dev server
npm start

# Build for production
npm run build
```

---

## Exercise List

| Category | Exercises |
|----------|-----------|
| Chest | Push-Up, Incline, Decline, Diamond, Wide |
| Back | Pull-Up, Chin-Up, Dead Hang, Row, Superman |
| Shoulders | Pike Push-Up, Lateral Raise, Front Raise, Shoulder Tap |
| Triceps | Dip, Bench Dip, Overhead Extension |
| Biceps | Curl, Hammer Curl, Concentration Curl |
| Legs | Squat, Lunge, Glute Bridge, Jump Squat, Pistol Squat, Calf Raise |
| Core | Plank, Hollow Body, Crunch, Mountain Climber, Leg Raise, Russian Twist |

---

## Deploy

Deployed automatically to Vercel on every push to `main`.

Firebase hosting also configured via `firebase.json`.
